  <text>
      <body>
        
     
      <div xml:id="ILoveYou"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="FreeVerse"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="happy"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="love"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
              <l>Her eyes were mostly shut. She didn't speak.</l>
          <l>The sun's slow exile crossed the wall above the bed.</l> 
          <l>But once, when I bent to feed her a drop</l>
          <l>of morphine from the little plastic beak,</l>
          <l>her hand shot up and gripped my arm. She looked right at me.</l>
          <l>When she said the words, it sounded like she meant: Dont leave</l>
          <l>me.</l>
          <l>From the very first, we love like this: our heads turning</l>
          <l>toward whatever mothers us, our mouths urgent</l>
          <l>for the taste of our name.</l>
         
                 
